${voffset -2}${color0}${font Hack:size=14}${font}${color}${goto 92}${voffset -6}Down: ${font Hack:style=Bold:size=8}${color1}${downspeed enp2s0}${color}
${voffset -2}${color0}${font Poky:size=13}w${font}${color}${goto 92}${voffset -4}Locale IP: ${alignr 300}${color2}${addr enp2s0}${color}

